REFERENCE           ANAKIN1
LANG_ENGLISH        "Hello, Snips."
LANG_CZECH          "Ahoj, Stekno."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN2
LANG_ENGLISH        "I didn't expect to see you so soon."
LANG_CZECH          "Necekal jsem, ze te uvidim tak brzy."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN3
LANG_ENGLISH        "You look old."
LANG_CZECH          "Vypadas starsi."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN4
LANG_ENGLISH        "You lost a fight!"
LANG_CZECH          "Prohrala jsi boj!"

REFERENCE           ANAKIN5
LANG_ENGLISH        "Trust me.. you lost."
LANG_CZECH          "Ver mi.. prohralas."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN6
LANG_ENGLISH        "So you do remember."
LANG_CZECH          "Takze si prece jen pamatujes."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN7
LANG_ENGLISH        "That's good."
LANG_CZECH          "To je dobre."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN8
LANG_ENGLISH        "It means you still have a chance."
LANG_CZECH          "Znamena to, ze mas porad sanci."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN9
LANG_ENGLISH        "To live.."
LANG_CZECH          "Zit.."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN10
LANG_ENGLISH        "I'm here to finish your training."
LANG_CZECH          "Jsem tady, abych dokoncil tvuj vycvik."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN11
LANG_ENGLISH        "One is never too old to learn, Snips."
LANG_CZECH          "Nikdy nejsi prilis stara na uceni, Stekno."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN12
LANG_ENGLISH        "Live.. or die!"
LANG_CZECH          "Zij.. nebo zemri!"

REFERENCE           ANAKIN13
LANG_ENGLISH        "I've heard that before."
LANG_CZECH          "To uz jsem nekdy slysel."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN14
LANG_ENGLISH        "I haven't thaught you everything yet!"
LANG_CZECH          "Jeste jsem te vse nenaucil!"

REFERENCE           ANAKIN15
LANG_ENGLISH        "You lack conviction!"
LANG_CZECH          "Chybi ti odhodlani!"

REFERENCE           ANAKIN16
LANG_ENGLISH        "Time to die!"
LANG_CZECH          "Cas zemrit!"

REFERENCE           ANAKIN17
LANG_ENGLISH        "There's hope for you yet."
LANG_CZECH          "Porad je v tobe nadeje."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN18
LANG_ENGLISH        "I don't know this battle."
