REFERENCE           ANAKIN19
LANG_ENGLISH        "Looks intense."
LANG_CZECH          "Vypada intenzivne."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN20
LANG_ENGLISH        "You did well."
LANG_CZECH          "Vedla sis dobre."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN21
LANG_ENGLISH        "You're a warrior now, as I trained you to be."
LANG_CZECH          "Ted uz jsi valecnice, tak jak jsem te vycvicil."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN22
LANG_ENGLISH        "Ahsoka, within you will be everything I am. All the knowledge I possess. Just as I inherited knowledge from my master and he from his. You're part of a legacy."
LANG_CZECH          "Ahsoko, v tobe bude vse, cim jsem ja. Vsechny me znalosti. Stejne jako jsem je zdedil od sveho mistra, a on od sveho. Jsi soucasti odkazu."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN23
LANG_ENGLISH        "But you're more than that, cause I'm more than that."
LANG_CZECH          "Ale jsi vic nez to, protoze ja jsem vic nez to."

REFERENCE           ANAKIN24
LANG_ENGLISH        "Is that what this is about?"
LANG_CZECH          "O tohle tady jde?"

